{"tid":633241,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(美食推介）麥當勞新出既至尊足三兩真係世界級","createTime":"2018-04-18T06:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T12:42:23.000Z","uid":165934,"like":5,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"27bd2bb51e77e47da4bfcd4607fbd75456f37cc7","tid":633241,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/18/144933_3a64bbb6094078a5e85441825e0d097e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F18%2F144933_3a64bbb6094078a5e85441825e0d097e.png&h=0f502eb2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多人話哩個包同舊既足三兩係一樣，你地真係大錯特錯了，淨係講塊130g既爆汁juicy牛肉已經唔可以同以前既足三兩比，全部食材都好新鮮，咬落去啖啖肉，真係太好食了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話咁快就食完個包，真係好正，一個真係唔夠，老闆！尼多個唔該！！！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/18/145520_48a3f5c4049494bd559be4fb5c2dc261.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F18%2F145520_48a3f5c4049494bd559be4fb5c2dc261.png&h=9c02c3f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c883fc11228faf9c6e33d06e413ef2014941e441","tid":633241,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"咁好食都有人負評，真係唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a295f25e4540867d2492677c0507b953ddf87e31","tid":633241,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"唔好再食牛牛了"},{"pid":"27b71a7fa4585885547d52c52c7d703ef26bbdae","tid":633241,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"咪即係至尊漢堡<br />\n改個名又賣貴d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebe915d40f7e174b46e025e93c20ba1f69590ae","tid":633241,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":